data.description: Come see this beautiful POOL home! With its perfect Location on the South side of Clermont, you will be able to get to the store, the State Park or any of Central Florida's main attractions with ease. As you walk in, you are greeted with elegant lighting, warm flooring, and a dreamy view of your private pool with no direct rear neighbors. A fully updated kitchen overlooks the main living area and allows you to feed and host with ease at all the family gatherings. Each bedroom can fit a large bed and has a designated bathroom. The large screened enclosure just had new screens installed. A beautiful new roof was installed last month! New facia around front of the home. Fresh exterior paint. All kitchen appliances and hot water heater are less than 2 years old! ITS LIKE ITS A BRAND NEW HOME! The community has its own pool, playground, basketball and tennis courts. It is a must see. Schedule your private showing today!
